        work that not only meets expectations but exceeds them. With 6 years of
        experience and a strong focus on detail, innovation, and efficiency, I
        bring value by aligning my expertise with business goals to create
        meaningful results.
      </text>

      <text class="text-lg">
        Collaboration is at the heart of what I do. Whether working with teams
        or clients, I strive to understand challenges, contribute strategic
        solutions, and ensure seamless execution. My approach is rooted in
